  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Tribe: Any tribe with Keen Smell.</p><p>Size: Any</p><p>You summon a Tracking Creature, trained to sense the more slightly scents.</p><p>When summoned, this creature will ask for a source. Something to use as a base to start tracking. From a piece of cloth, to blood.</p><p>This creature then will make a Wisdom (Perception) check at advantage, utilizing the base Wisdom Ability Modifier for their Tribe. This creature counts as having Expertice on perception as they train for this specific</p><p>For each aditional rank above base, increase the Wisdom Ability Modifier by 2.</p>",
